"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1930990-sailing-abandoned-wind-olympic-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A bewilderedBBCcommentator was left stunned when anOlympicevent came to a standstill, not once but twice.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's skiff medal race, featuring Team GB, was in full swing when it was abruptly stopped by organisers.\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 146, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9674734343564207, \"rank\": 0.03334787541328186, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The drama unfolded because of a sudden and dramatic shift in the wind's direction, potentially skewing the competition in some teams' favour.\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite a swift restart, the race was soon stopped again because of a lack of wind.\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The race could be rescheduled for Friday, which could be good news for Team GB, who were down in sixth place at the time of the first stoppage.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 516, \"end\": 523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9674734343564207, \"rank\": 0.03334787541328186, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BBC sailing commentator Niall Myant expressed his astonishment at the development, saying: \\\"I have never seen that in a medal race at the Olympic level.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9913220288937734, \"rank\": 0.00835764762107009, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can only imagine it's because the breeze has drifted so dramatically, the committee have decided it's unfair so they have abandoned the race.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Quite the moment.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That would have been a really hard decision.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These are the best of the best, they train and work at this.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They commit themselves to making the playing field as level as possible and they obviously felt that it was unworkable.\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was pushing boats forward that should not have been there and they have decided to let this one go.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Great Britain were not having the greatest race.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1239, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9969232274011721, \"rank\": 0.0019480344664750495, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot believe we have abandoned a medal race.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a shorter race, so you normally only need one small patch in the wind.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the race management team are saying, 'we got this one wrong'.\\\"\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think for Spain, it will be a blow but for some of the other teams, it will be a lifeline.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9604671533191758, \"rank\": 0.018286032096980827, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand will take this as a relief.\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.7333260068817244, \"rank\": 0.3584403284237645, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The conversation here can not be wait too long here, you need to just wait for the next one.\\\"\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The stoppage also left many viewers bemused but former Ireland Olympic sailing medallist Annalise Murphy offered some clarity on the situation.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9997821607149731, \"rank\": 0.00021788386681930594, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annalise_Murphy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Annalise Murphy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annalise_Murphy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annalise_Murphy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told RTE: \\\"In sailing you are dealing with the elements, the wind, the waves.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was a very light-wind race and you could start to see that it was getting a bit unfair.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 2033, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The race committee clearly decided it was unfair.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are Olympic medals at stake.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard to run a race like that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2507, \"end\": 2512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999962792572, \"rank\": 3.7207679488790358e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2588, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9993700377048167, \"rank\": 0.0006303593030689078, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A